   "source": [
    "### Check Voting Eligibility"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "29850fa3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "You can vote\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "age = 20\n",
    "is_citizen = True\n",
    "\n",
    "if age >= 18 and is_citizen:\n",
    "    print(\"You can vote\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"You can't vote\")    "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "47d0d976",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### `or` – Truth Table\n",
    "\n",
    "| A | B | A or B | Result |\n",
    "|---|---|--------|--------|\n",
    "| `True` | `True` | `True` |  True |\n",
    "| `True` | `False` | `True` | True |\n",
    "| `False` | `True` | `True` | True |\n",
    "| `False` | `False` | `False` | False |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Quick Examples\n",
    "\n",
    "| Condition | Code | Result |\n",
    "|-----------|------|--------|\n",
    "| Both true | `(5 > 3) or (2 < 4)` | `True` |\n",
    "| First true | `(5 > 3) or (2 > 4)` | `True` |\n",
    "| Second true | `(5 < 3) or (2 < 4)` | `True` |\n",
    "| Both false | `(5 < 3) or (2 > 4)` | `False` |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d2f6ce8b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Weekend Check"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "1734b4c9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "It's a working day!\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "day = \"Monday\"\n",
    "\n",
    "if day == \"Friday\" or day == \"Saturday\":\n",
    "    print(\"It's the weekend!\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"It's a working day!\")  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e1cb021f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### `not` – Truth Table\n",
    "\n",
    "| A | not A |\n",
    "|---|-------|\n",
    "| `True` | `False` |\n",
    "| `False` | `True` | \n",
    "\n",
    "### Quick Examples\n",
    "\n",
    "| Condition | Code | Result |\n",
    "|-----------|------|--------|\n",
    "| Not true | `not (5 > 3)` | `False` |\n",
    "| Not false | `not (5 < 3)` | `True` |\n",
    "| Not equal | `not x == 5` | Equivalent to `x != 5` |\n",
    "| Not empty | `not my_list` | `True` if empty |\n",
    "\n",
   
   ]
  },
